This is a big commit regarding a huge flaw with the model for dealing with an eclipse VFS. Specifically  multiple eclipse file links can in fact point to the same absolute file  so using the absolute file as a key to map backwards to an eclipse-based path is unacceptable and can yield more than one answer.  This commit will cause archives unit test regressions  which I will work on fixing.  git-svn-id: http://svn.jboss.org/repos/jbosstools/trunk@8977 a97e2381-89e5-4abb-bab3-167db6db766c
